        "WRISTLET": "An elastic band worn around the wrist, as for the purpose ofsecuring the upper part of a glove.",
        "WRIT": "3d pers. sing. pres. of Write, for writeth. Chaucer.",
        "WRITABILITY": "Ability or capacity to write. [R.] Walpole.",
